The '''Luf Virus''' was a particularly offensive, communicable disease that affected most [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoid]] races. It originated on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[M'haeli/Legends|M'haeli]], and flourished in cities and ghettos.

